elements.title: Ganesh idol at Khairatabad
elements.contents: ... that the height of the Ganesh idol at Khairatabad in India increased by one foot (0.3 m) every year between 1954 and 2014?

elements.title: Warwick Railway
elements.contents: ... that the Warwick Railway successfully operated independently for decades despite having just three employees, two locomotives, and less than a mile (1.6 km) of track?
